According to **FastAPI latest**, the template logic should be:

```jinja2
{% if github_sponsors %}
  {% for group in github_sponsors.sponsors %}
    {% for user in group %}
      {% if user.login not in sponsors_badge.logins %}
@{{ user.login }}
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
